Is inference is the next defining challenge—and opportunity—for enterprise AI?

@Lenovodc 's Scott Tease breaks down why inference is the moment AI actually delivers value—when employees get more productive, customers get better experiences, and loyalty is built in real time. Training has dominated the conversation for years. But deploying AI into live operations is a completely different game defined by latency, reliability, and scale.

That’s the shift driving Lenovo’s AI inferencing server portfolio: AI that runs at the speed of real life, where people actually experience it. https://t.co/cTV1LLNKlw

